race.comment: NORTHERN PRIDE (2) loves it here around this circuit with four wins and five placings from just 11 spins and has been racing very consistently of late. Rates among the leading chances. FODOR (3) grows a leg for hoop Wiggins who has four wins and four placings from 11 steers. Can go back-to-back without surprising. The well-related BRASCO (5) (half to G2 winner Blueberry Hill) has only missed a drum once in four efforts over this course and distance and gets some weight off with the claim. Top-three aspirations. ACROPHOBIC (1) is a three-time winner over this seven-furlong journey and has claims on best figures. DILLINGER (4) rounds out the selections.
